result.name: The Coffee Academics Taikoo Park

reviews.text:
Went for breakfast and it was the best continental breakfast I have had in a long time. The serving was huge although never felt very full (was just nice, probably because of the sour dough bread that was served). 

The chicken was really tender and the serving was very thoughtful. 

Variety of coffee’s for coffee lovers and enjoyed mine! Probably a bit on the higher side of cost, but definitely worth the visit :)

I actually really like this restaurant.
Very nice coffee and got options of oat milk and soy milk.
Food is quite delicious too but a bit pricy for the portion. 
Nice decoration and staff is super nice.
Joined their membership program and got some good discounts from time to time.
It has been my third visit in one month.

A saving grace on a difficult morning. Although I would consider it pricey in comparison to most places in Hong Kong they are committed to presentation. Coffee was second to none and I had an enjoyable plate of blueberry pancakes.
Didn't like the flavour of the espresso (personal taste).  Much too fruity/acidic.
It is very awesome coffee shop! Very good mood and food , coffee. The staff was especially kind. We eat agave, avocado toast and espresso butter pancake. If we visit hk, will be back !!

reviews.text:
I like to enjoy some simple cafe food and a cup of coffee facing fantastic mountains view through big windows.  The ceiling is high and environment is quiet. Serving simple quick bite  food, wine and bakery. 

Unfortunately, they use disposal utensils which are not user-friendly, in my opinion. Be alert! Weekend will be closed.
Pretty good view and nice location. Easy to get to central. Service is good, facilities are fresh and modern. Five stars recommendation!
Nice environment on the outside. Not a fan of the futuristic elevator and interior design. I just can’t tell where it’s wall and where it’s door
Great companies offering venues as part of CSR.
Nice building and the area near the building is very nice. You can get indian food, cofee and other items nearby.
